{"tid":877525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫克：個人數據已成軍事武器","createTime":"2018-10-26T11:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T12:20:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7faac4543026910aa75be2b8e64dccf6e4433799","tid":877525,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181026/20531129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F20531129&d=oebe6V3AXpIM2Uzdd4pUczANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=90d96ba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F20531129&h=f0a4422f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181026/20531129</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月26日 <br />\n<br />\n庫克：個人數據已成軍事武器<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181026/large/26wf02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F26wf02p.jpg&h=3a6b329f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n庫克指個人資料已被用作「武器」。<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果行政總裁庫克（Tim Cook）指極敏感的個人數據已被用作攻擊美國的軍事武器，「我們不應以糖衣包裝這後果，這是活脫脫的監控」。他又盛讚歐盟5月落實的《一般資料保護規則》（GDPR），促美國跟隨立法規管業界對個人資料的處理手法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促落實全面私隱條例<br />\n<br />\n庫克日前到布魯塞爾出席有關資訊保安及網絡私隱的國際會議發言時，指個人數據的買賣已成產業鏈，科技公司和廣告商不惜投放數十億元去追蹤人們讚好或討厭甚麼、人們的願望和恐懼，「我們應該為此而感到不安」。他又指歐盟的GDPR更能保障人民私隱，「蘋果支持美國落實全面的私隱條例」。<br />\n<br />\n開放權利運動（Open Rights Group）總監基洛克（Jim Killock）形容，庫克的發言對推動美國立法保障私隱「十分重要」，「當然亦可能是出於商業利益的考量，因近年網絡保安事故頻生，美國公司正失去客戶的信任」。<br />\n<br />\n英國曼徹斯特大學教授埃利奧特（Mark Elliot）則認為庫克做得不夠，「真正的數碼科技民主，應是用戶對個人資料的運用有話事權」。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n手機易截聽　普京、習近平避用<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n沙地王儲譴責殺記者暴行：感到痛心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部：擔心就用華為<br />\n<br />\n手機易截聽　普京、習近平避用<br />\n<br />\n中俄勾線　竊聽特朗普iPhone向朋友圈埋手制訂對付策略"},{"pid":"86e3305b37d7156f491693618525e4ef1c2f3151","tid":877525,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"雲上貴州？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f76df0ed9952f1d2a0971c6a1adb4b8381daf3","tid":877525,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e3305b37d7156f491693618525e4ef1c2f3151","tid":877525,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"雲上貴州？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:20:57.000Z","msg":"ifan: 睇唔到睇唔到，google仲衰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}